'''別克Envision'''（Buick Envision）是[[通用汽车|通用汽车]]旗下品牌[[别克|别克]]汽車開發製造的中型[[運動型多用途車|運動型多用途車]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://auto.163.com/14/0909/09/A5MLNI2F00084TUR_all.html |title=定价决定成败 试驾上海通用别克昂科威 |accessdate=2016-07-24 |archive-date=2016-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814220432/http://auto.163.com/14/0909/09/A5MLNI2F00084TUR_all.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[跨界休旅車|跨界休旅車]]，官方中文名稱為「'''別克昂科威'''」，而競爭對手為[[本田Avancier|本田Avancier]]、[[豐田Highlander|豐田Highlander]]、[[福特Edge|福特Edge]]、[[日產Murano|日產Murano]]。

== 歷史與概要 ==
=== 第一代（2014年）===
2014年8月，別克昂科威在成都车展全球首发亮相。2015年12月，别克昂科威成为[[上汽通用|上汽通用]]首批整车出口北美市场的车型<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mt.sohu.com/20160120/n435252201.shtml |title=“中国制造”昂科威出口北美 |accessdate=2016-07-24 |archive-date=2016-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820025608/http://mt.sohu.com/20160120/n435252201.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美国市場上，别克昂科威于2016年1月11日在[[底特律車展|底特律車展]]上首次亮相。<ref>[http://www.autoblog.com/2016/01/11/2016-buick-envision-detroit-2016/ "2016 Buick Envision might be your first Chinese-built crossover"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.autoblog.com/2016/01/11/2016-buick-envision-detroit-2016/ |date=20211026043312 }} from Autoblog (January 11, 2016)</ref>

===2019年款===
2019年别克昂科威于2017年底在中国首次亮相，并于2018年在北美市场亮相。<ref>[http://gmauthority.com/blog/2018/02/2019-buick-envision-bows-with-updated-looks-and-customer-focused-improvements/ “2019 Buick Envision Bows With Updated Looks And Customer Focused Improvements”] {{Wayback|url=http://gmauthority.com/blog/2018/02/2019-buick-envision-bows-with-updated-looks-and-customer-focused-improvements/ |date=20211025221626 }} from GM Authority (February 26, 2018)</ref>

===2020年款===
2020年款于2020年初在中国首次亮相<ref>[https://gmauthority.com/blog/2019/10/images-of-2020-buick-envision-facelift-for-china-surface/#:~:text=Under%20the%20hood%20of%20the,185%20pound%2Dfeet%20of%20torque.&text=The%202.5%2Dliter%20engine%20is,with%20the%20nine%2Dspeed%20auto. “Images Of 2020 Buick Envision Facelift For China Surface”] {{Wayback|url=https://gmauthority.com/blog/2019/10/images-of-2020-buick-envision-facelift-for-china-surface/#:~:text=Under%20the%20hood%20of%20the,185%20pound%2Dfeet%20of%20torque.&text=The%202.5%2Dliter%20engine%20is,with%20the%20nine%2Dspeed%20auto. |date=20211026043314 }} from GM Authority (October 21, 2019)</ref>

=== 第二代（2021年）===
2020年5月，[[通用汽車|通用汽車]]在美国推出了第二代别克昂科威<ref name="gen2">{{cite web |title=Buick has given the Envision a sharp redesign |publisher=Autoblog |author=Zac Palmer |date=May 29, 2020 |url=https://www.autoblog.com/2020/05/29/2021-buick-envision |access-date=2021-10-22 |archive-date=2021-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025221038/https://www.autoblog.com/2020/05/29/2021-buick-envision/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 昂科威Plus====
2021年上海车展期间推出的昂科威Plus是昂科威的加长版。<ref>{{cite web|title=https://www.motor1.com/news/502025/buick-envision-plus-verano-debut-china/|publisher=motor1.com|author=Christopher Smith|date=2021-04-19|url=Buick Envision Plus SUV, Verano Pro Sedan Debut At Auto Shanghai}}</ref>

